SavedModel builder.

<!-- Placeholder for "Used in" -->

Builds a SavedModel that can be saved to storage, is language neutral, and
enables systems to produce, consume, or transform TensorFlow Models.

## Classes

[`class SavedModelBuilder`](../../../../tf/saved_model/Builder): Builds the `SavedModel` protocol buffer and saves variables and assets.
